  "title": "ISic001082. I.Sicily inscription 001082",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Πολυστεφάνῳ\n                    Σωτείρᾳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"epithet\" data-text=\"Πολυστεφάνῳ\">Πολυστεφάνῳ</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σωτείρᾳ\">Σωτείρᾳ</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νικομήδης ὁ καὶ\n                    Ὄνυς\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νικομήδης\">Νικομήδης</span> ὁ καὶ <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὄνυς\">Ὄνυς</span></span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"ΣωτίρᾳΣωτείρᾳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ΣωτίρᾳΣωτείρᾳ\">Σωτίρᾳ</span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\">l.4 reg., orig. ΣΩΤΙΡΑΙΣωτίρᾳ</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Πολυστεφάνῳ\n                    Σωτείρᾳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"epithet\" data-text=\"Πολυστεφάνῳ\">ΠΟΛΥΣΤΕΦΑΝΩ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σωτείρᾳ\">ΣΩΤΕΙΡΑ</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νικομήδης ὁ καὶ\n                    Ὄνυς\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Νικομήδης\">ΝΙΚΟΜΗΔΗΣ</span>ΟΚΑΙ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ὄνυς\">ΟΝΥΣ</span></span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"ΣωτίρᾳΣωτείρᾳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ΣωτίρᾳΣωτείρᾳ\">ΣΩΤΙΡΑ</span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.4 reg., orig. ΣΩΤΙΡΑΙΣωτίρᾳ</p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001082_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Archeologico Regionale P. Griffo, Agrigento\" src=\"ISic001082_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001082.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Archeologico Regionale P. Griffo, Agrigento\" src=\"ISic001082-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001082_copy2_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Archeologico Regionale P. Griffo, Agrigento\" src=\"ISic001082_copy2_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001082_copy2.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Archeologico Regionale P. Griffo, Agrigento\" src=\"ISic001082_copy2-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001082_leftthreequarter_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Archeologico Regionale P. Griffo, Agrigento\" src=\"ISic001082_leftthreequarter_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001082_leftthreequarter.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Archeologico Regionale P. Griffo, Agrigento\" src=\"ISic001082_leftthreequarter-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic001082_rear_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Archeologico Regionale P. Griffo, Agrigento\" src=\"ISic001082_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001082_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, courtesy Museo Archeologico Regionale P. Griffo, Agrigento\" src=\"ISic001082_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text from autopsy</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 35.0996 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 1968.0607 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282</a></li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">262</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> De Waele 1971 33 no.4 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002040\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002040</a></li></ul>  <ul><li> Dubois 1989 205 n.67 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187</a></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>The first two lines are deeply incised, the second two very lightly incised. Alpha has straight bar, with an apex; epsilon has equal length horizontals; mu in line 3 has extended apices, in anticipation of the cursive form; omicron is circular in lines 1 and 3, angular (made up of straight lines) in lines 3 and 4; sigma is and open four bar sigma in lines 1-2, a quadrate lunate sigma in lines 3-4; phi has a small elongated eye; omega is open in lines 1-2, lunate in line 4. It is therefore likely that lines 1-2 were incised by a different hand from lines 3-4.</p> Line 1  6-15  Line 2  9-16  Line 3  5-8  Line 4  6-14  Interlineation line 1 to 2  9-12  Interlineation line 2 to 3  5-9  Interlineation line 3 to 4  2-5  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
